:FED.
3.6. Translation of currency at businesses abroad
.br
(Dynamic Currency Conversion)
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If you use your card abroad, the business may offer to perform
a currency conversion before the payment transaction is
processed. Before you approve this, you must ask the business
to state which charges will be applied, and what exchange rate
will be used for the conversion. Please note that the exchange
rate applied by the business may be different from that applied
by &BANKNAVN., and that &BANKNAVN. has no influence on the
exchange rate applied by the business.
