event of any claims handling.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The information can otherwise be used by &BANKNAVN. as your card
issuer to send you advantageous offers on hotel accommodation, travel
and airline tickets, for example. The material you
receive from &BANKNAVN. may contain marketing of other
companies' products. The information may also be used to send
you customer magazines, information about partners and new
supplementary services, as well as various special offers.
