5. Issuing a warning if the card or PIN code is lost or misused, or if
an unauthorised person has come into possession of the card
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
When &BANKNAVN. has been informed that the card has been
lost or that another person has learned the associated
PIN code, &BANKNAVN. will cancel the card immediately. In
addition, use of the card will be blocked in the NETS and
MasterCard authorisation systems if &BANKNAVN. considers
this action necessary to prevent misuse. Similarly, the
card will be blocked if &BANKNAVN. has grounds to suspect
misuse.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You will be informed in writing that your card has been blocked, along
with a statement of the time at which &BANKNAVN. was requested to impose
the block.
